自由探索小玩具 激發好奇心
手作りのおもちゃで自由な遊びを

platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.st.k: Pok Pok Playroom’s married founders set out to create a kids’ app parents wouldn’t have to mute in a restaurant—and to the delight of grown-up diners everywhere, they did it. Pok Pok Playroom is a free-play feast for little senses: There are switches to flip, gears to grind, and blobs to plop together, all drawn and designed by hand to make the app feel like a tactile, handcrafted toy. Endlessly inventive but never overwhelming, it’s a master class in how a simple app can sometimes feel the most advanced.
這個專為小朋友而設的免費遊戲盛宴聲音柔和，即使身處公共場合也無需將裝置調成靜音。小朋友可以盡情翻轉開關、研磨齒輪、組合斑點等，App 以簡單易懂的畫面，展現無限的前衛創意。
这是玩具，不是游戏，只为寻找乐趣。开关可以翻转，齿轮可以磨碎，水滴会扑通一声落在一起，小朋友在自由探索中释放无穷创造力。柔和的背景音让孩子安静地沉浸其中。

An app parents won’t have to mute in a restaurant, this is a free-play feast with switches to flip, gears to grind and blobs to plop together. Endlessly inventive, it’s a master class in how a simple app can sometimes feel the most advanced.s
這是一款你不必擔心音量的兒童 App。孩子可以在這款看似簡單、實則先進的 App 中，翻轉開關、轉動齒輪、組合各種元素，盡情發揮創意。

An app parents won’t have to mute in a restaurant, this is a free-play feast with switches to flip, gears to grind, and blobs to plop together. Endlessly inventive, it’s a master class in how a simple app can sometimes feel the most advanced.
レストランで保護者が音を消さなくていい、自由な遊びが豊富にそろっているアプリです。スイッチを押して反転させたり、歯車を回したり、かたまり同士をくっつけたりして楽しめます。シンプルなアプリが驚くほど高度に感じられる、創意工夫に富んだアプリです。
